Hello, I am Lamp! I am multi-passionate and struggling with the thought of how much the universe contains and how little time I get to experience it. But then I remember my cat, my partner, frieands & family, and I feel like I am experiencing the most important parts. I am sort of contructing my own little universe with them in the centre and so much more around it.

Hoping that I will find people with different world views and ideas so that I just dont build my own echo chamber. Wish me luck :)
